title: Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
